<pb ed="ZW" xml:id="ZW09.0073c.0070a" n="0070a"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">錄文三</cb:mulu><head>〔錄文三〕</head>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a02"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a03"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a0301">（前殘）</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a04"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a0401">經云：「有持戒修福者」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a05"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0070a0501" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">尸羅得清淨，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">無量劫來因。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a06"/><l style="text-indent:2em">妄想如怨賊，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">貪愛若參辰。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a07"/><l style="text-indent:2em">在欲而無欲，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">居塵不染塵。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a08"/><l style="text-indent:2em">但依離垢<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0070001" n="0070001"/>地，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">當證法王身。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a09"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a10"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a1001">□…□</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a11"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0070a1101" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">□…□，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">大聖□□□。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a12"/><l style="text-indent:2em">□…□，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">定入法王家。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a13"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a14"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a1401">經云：「離一切諸相，即名諸佛」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a15"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0070a1501" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">如能發心者，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">應當遠二邊。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a16"/><l style="text-indent:2em">涅槃無有相，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">菩薩離能詮。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a17"/><l style="text-indent:2em">無乘及乘者，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">人法兩俱捐。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a18"/><l style="text-indent:2em">欲達無生忍，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">應當絕大源。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a19"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a20"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a2001">經云：「如是」至「第一波羅蜜」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a21"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0070a2101" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">波羅稱彼岸，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">於中十種名。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a22"/><l style="text-indent:2em">高卑緣妄識，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">次第為迷情。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a23"/><l style="text-indent:2em">燄裏尋求水，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">琴中覓響聲。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a24"/><l style="text-indent:2em">真如何得失，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">今乃號圓成。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a25"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0070a26"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0070a2601">經云：「如我昔為歌利王」至「應生嗔恨」</p>
<pb ed="ZW" xml:id="ZW09.0073c.0071a" n="0071a"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a01"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0071a0101" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">暴虐誰無道，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">時稱歌離王。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a02"/><l style="text-indent:2em">逢軍出遊獵，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">仙人橫被傷。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a03"/><l style="text-indent:2em">已經五百歲，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">前後極時長。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a04"/><l style="text-indent:2em">乘斯忍辱力，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">今乃證真常。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a05"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a06"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0071a0601">經云：「不應住色生心，不應住色布施」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a07"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0071a0701" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">菩薩行深智，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">何曾不帶悲。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a08"/><l style="text-indent:2em">投身飼餓虎，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">割肉濟鷹饑。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a09"/><l style="text-indent:2em">精勤三大劫，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">曾無一念疲。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a10"/><l style="text-indent:2em">如能行此行，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">皆作四生師。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a11"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a12"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0071a1201">經云：「真語，不異語」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a13"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0071a1301" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">眾生與<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0071001" n="0071001"/>蘊界，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">名別體非<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0071002" n="0071002"/>殊。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a14"/><l style="text-indent:2em">了心知是幻，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">迷情見有無。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a15"/><l style="text-indent:2em">真言言不妄，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">實語語非虛。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a16"/><l style="text-indent:2em">始終無變易，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">性相本來如。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a17"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a18"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0071a1801">經云：「如來所得法無實無虛」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a19"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0071a1901" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">證空便為實，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">執無乃成虛。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a20"/><l style="text-indent:2em">非真亦非假，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">誰有復誰無。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a21"/><l style="text-indent:2em">對病應須藥，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">病癒<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0071003" n="0071003"/>藥還除。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a22"/><l style="text-indent:2em">常依般若觀，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">凝寂契真如。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a23"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0071a24"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0071a2401">經云：「初日分」至「其福勝彼」</p>
<pb ed="ZW" xml:id="ZW09.0073c.0072a" n="0072a"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a01"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0072a0101" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">眾生與人我，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">蘊上執虛名。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a02"/><l style="text-indent:2em">如龜毛不實，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">似兔角無形。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a03"/><l style="text-indent:2em">捨身緣妄識，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">施命為愚情。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a04"/><l style="text-indent:2em">未離人無我，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">何以證圓成。</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a05"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a06"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0072a0601">經云：「如來為發大乘、最上乘者」</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a07"/><lg xml:id="lgZW09p0072a0701" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:2em">所作皆依性，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">修成功德林。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a08"/><l style="text-indent:2em">終無趣寂滅，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">唯□□□□。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a09"/><l style="text-indent:2em">□□□□□，</l><l style="text-indent:0em">用<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0072001" n="0072001"/>智智慧深。</l>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a10"/><l style="text-indent:2em">利□…□</l></lg>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a11"/><p style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em" xml:id="pZW09p0072a1101">（下殘）</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a12"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0072a13"/><p xml:id="pZW09p0072a1301">〔錄文完〕</p></cb:div>
</body>
